data.description: Discover the epitome of modern comfort in this exceptional townhome strategically situated just moments away from picturesque Historic Roswell, Roswell & Leita Thompson Parks, and a plethora of shopping.  A harmonious blend of convenience and luxury awaits within this thoughtfully designed residence.  Step inside to an inviting open floorplan, fostering seamless interactions between the kitchen, dining spaces, and the welcoming great room. The see-through fireplace serves as the centerpiece, not only keeping you cozy but also creating an ambiance that's perfect for any occasion.  There is, also, a powder room, entrance foyer, and deck on this level. Upstairs, revel in the expansive space of two generously sized suites, each boasting its own en-suite bath, providing unparalleled comfort and privacy and in the hallway is a convenient laundry closet. Both the main and upstairs levels have hardwood flooring.  The upstairs primary bathroom does have a soaking tub, separate tiled shower, double granite vanity, private water closet and large walk-in closet. The finished terrace level with new carpet elevates your living experience, offering a versatile space ideal for game-day festivities, guest accommodations, or simply unwinding after a long day. Complete with a full bath this space offers an opportunity for a true third private suite.  This floorplan with three very spacious and private suites is ideal for roommates.  This home embodies modern elegance with its array of upgrades, including hardwood flooring, all walls freshly painted, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The gated neighborhood ensures security and tranquility and has easy access to the Interstate 400.  Schedule a viewing today and embrace the lifestyle this townhome has to offer.
